p: Alexander S Hughes David Hughes James Boyd David Hart and Joseph Brannan
Defendants except to Sheriff return and say that he claims to hold them under said commitment the same is illegal.

For that these defendants never threatened to destroy to injure and destroy the property of of Josiah Gellerson and Geroge Gellerson as in any way on the 5th day of May or at any other time infor which they were convicted and upon which said commitment was issued
Alex S. Hughes David D. Hughes David Hart James Boyd Joseph Brannon
Subscribed and Sworn to before me this 15h day of May 1875 }
